          <h1>Features</h1>

          <h2 class="header-medium">Map View</h2>
          <p>The Map View allows users to select areas that they would like to create profiles for. Further, users can examine geographic characteristics that may inform the selection of areas to be profiled. (For example, a user can locate the tract in which a particular address may be found by using the Search feature in conjunction with the Census Tract Geographic Summary Level.)</p>
          </div>

