            <div class="cell medium-9 large-10">
              <p>The Search input provides various types of results as you type. Search for known addresses, specific buildings (like the American Museum of Natural History), subway stops (like Broadway Junction), and neighborhoods (like Crown Heights).</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="header-medium">Selection (click on geography)</h3>
