            <div class="cell medium-9 large-10">
              <p>The Selection feature adds geographies (like census tracts) for inclusion in profile output. Once a selection has been made, users can go to the Profile View to examine the population, socioeconomic, and housing characteristics. Users can add to a selected area by left-clicking on unselected geographies. Users can remove geographies from a selection by left-clicking on selected geographies.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
