            <div class="cell medium-9 large-10">
              <p>Advanced Options encompass features that can inform a user’s geographic selection. The Thematic Maps feature provides users with Neighborhood Tabulation Area overlay maps for selected variables. Other overlay features include: Subway System (showing an overlay of all subway lines and stations), Community District (CD) boundaries, New York City Council District boundaries, Neighborhood Tabulation Area (NTA) boundaries, Public Use Microdata Area (PUMA) boundaries, and Borough boundaries.</p>
            </div>
