          <h2 class="header-medium">Profile View</h2>
          <p>The Profile View allows users to examine all data output for their selected area.</p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="header-medium">Profile Tabs</h3>
          <div class="grid-x">
            <div class="cell medium-3 large-2 feature-image-cell">
              {{!-- TODO: Edit this placeholder image! --}}
