            </div>
            <div class="cell medium-9 large-10">
              <p>Profile Tabs permit users to switch between different data sources and profile types – There are five profile tabs: Census – showing basic demographic and housing data from the decennial censuses); Demographic (ACS) – providing users with basic population statistics from the American Community Survey; Social (ACS) – social characteristics from the American Community Survey; Economic (ACS) – economic characteristics from the American Community Survey; and Housing (ACS) – detailed housing characteristics from the American Community Survey.</p>
            </div>
          </div>          

